about.summary: Along US-166, this casual hotel in a commercial area with shops and eateries is 1 mile from the early 20th-century Brown Mansion. It's a 7-minute walk from the Dalton Defenders and Coffeyville History Museum, and 4 miles from the Coffeyville Aviation Heritage Museum. Warmly decorated rooms feature Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, as well as minifridges, microwaves and coffeemakers. Suites add in-room whirlpool tubs, and separate living areas with sofabeds. Amenities include a fitness center, an indoor heated pool and a hot tub, plus guest laundry facilities. Breakfast and parking are available.
